{"id":149912,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/哈马斯和法塔赫实现和解/","date":"2011-05-05T01:30:30Z","modified":"2011-05-05T01:30:30Z","title":"哈马斯和法塔赫实现和解","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">开罗</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">巴勒斯坦组织法塔赫和哈马斯经过长达</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年的分裂后实现和解。双方代表在开罗签署了一项协议，协议中规定，成立一个共同的过渡政府并在今年举行新的大选。但协议中没有提及未来如何控制双方的安全力量，以及如何处理同以色列的关系。政治上温和的法塔赫和政治上极端的哈马斯实现和解是成立一个独立的巴勒斯坦国最为重要的前提条件。另有</span><span>11</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个较小的巴勒斯坦组织也加入了开罗协议。埃及在法塔赫和哈马斯之间的调解中发挥了重要作用。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15049952%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%93%88%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%92%8C%E6%B3%95%E5%A1%94%E8%B5%AB%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%A3\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}